{"tid":2273353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬雲講錯嘢得罪官    痛失五百億","createTime":"2020-11-05T16:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T20:29:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c39b142c92315401b844c5af0d7e60c45d297116","tid":2273353,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/W.bXe5FbJhCAem7BhZHCFA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMy42/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/7cMIylo9RPD1XhQbbcMwig--~B/aD00NDY7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/9bbc31710a410ecf9c444068474fb8d0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FW.bXe5FbJhCAem7BhZHCFA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMy42%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7cMIylo9RPD1XhQbbcMwig--~B%2FaD00NDY7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F9bbc31710a410ecf9c444068474fb8d0&h=a5b2e041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n螞蟻集團（06688，688688.SH）上市被煞停的原因，市場有多種揣測。有指是馬雲在10月底上海外灘金融峰會的演講「出事」，當中對監管、對中國銀行體系很有看法。之後11月2日迎來內地4部門聯合約談馬雲等螞蟻集團有關人員，官媒於同日暗諷「話不可隨口」。<br />\n<br />\n阿里市值單日蒸發4891億<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴（09988）周三股價大瀉，市值單日蒸發了4,891.79億元，以馬雲持股4.8%計，他個人身家便輸掉234.8億元。另外，螞蟻原本上市A+H股市值合計約3,100億元，如今上市落空，以馬雲持股8.8%計，他有272.8億元落空了。合計起來，馬雲一席話，可謂盛惠507.6億元！<br />\n<br />\n話說上述10月底金融峰會期間，馬雲以聯合國數字合作高級別小組聯合主席身份演講，言論多次觸及銀行體系和監管，批評「今天的銀行延續的還是當舖思想」，「要麼是資產全押了出去，壓力巨大；要麼肆無忌憚貸款，不斷加槓桿，負債搞得很大」。他又批評，「銀行喜歡給好企業、不需要錢的企業貸款，結果讓很多好企業變成了壞企業，形成了多元化的投資，錢太多也惹很多事」。<br />\n<br />\n官媒隨後在11月2日發表文章，以15字真言《話不可隨口，事不可隨心，人不可隨意》為題作出暗諷，3句開首字合讀起來就是「話事人」3字，雖然全篇沒有點名馬雲或阿里等，但配相卻是一張「馬形狀的雲」在天上飄，被網民形容為「馬雲飄了」之意。該篇官媒文章直言「人哪能隨心所欲地活着，所有的自由都是相對和需要付出代價的」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yAu7VdetT9NaMLKsRfYCpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/feb310f4c71576c5132e8064013a7871\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyAu7VdetT9NaMLKsRfYCpg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Ffeb310f4c71576c5132e8064013a7871&h=874d936d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/馬雲-席話-痛失五百億-214500693.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%A6%AC%E9%9B%B2-%E5%B8%AD%E8%A9%B1-%E7%97%9B%E5%A4%B1%E4%BA%94%E7%99%BE%E5%84%84-214500693.html&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=3110c4ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/馬雲-席話-痛失五百億-214500693.html</a>"},{"pid":"03f053d6bb81df5a68d3e4d44f726c0fbfbc7547","tid":2273353,"uid":355289,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"堆手續費同孖展息係咪螞蟻食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果道好似成1.3萬億"},{"pid":"e7059e4fcf2d251b034a4e1d138857d51798b859","tid":2273353,"uid":47222,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"03f053d6bb81df5a68d3e4d44f726c0fbfbc7547","tid":2273353,"uid":355289,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"堆手續費同孖展息係咪螞蟻食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果道好似成1.3萬億"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"孖展又唔係螞蟻借出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fe6b960e82d35814f35bd2bbcf6615914e1126","tid":2273353,"uid":263261,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"03f053d6bb81df5a68d3e4d44f726c0fbfbc7547","tid":2273353,"uid":355289,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"堆手續費同孖展息係咪螞蟻食哂<img src=\"/ass